deactivate WorkoutList #FFBBBB
":Run" --> Parser: newRun:Run
deactivate ":Run" #FFBBBB

Parser -> Output : printAddRun()
activate Output #FFBBBB
Output --> User:
deactivate Output #FFBBBB
